Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.73,0:00:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a message from GreatBen810.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.90,0:00:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"Are you going to the release event?"
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.30,0:00:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely, I wouldn't miss it.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.67,0:00:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, GreatBen810?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.90,0:00:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that was fast!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.21,0:00:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm gonna make it, no matter what. This is the first chance we've ever gotten to meet Annabel."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.55,0:00:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.05,0:00:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish it was Saturday already!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.95,0:00:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You three again?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.69,0:00:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It was condemnable of you to sneak\Ninto the kitchen and pilfer a pie!{## you can make this edit unhappen again. deplorable is probably the best word we can use here, but i'd rather not produce fodder for meme captions}{I actually used deplorable and nasty in a single script after that stuff, and nobody noticed}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.19,0:00:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention you wolfed the entire thing down in a single night!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.95,0:00:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not ashamed as students of Luna Nova?! {the three segment thing really bugs me}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.33,0:00:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I told you to take something less conspicuous.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.95,0:00:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a pie.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.31,0:01:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.20,0:01:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't take a pie. It was a tart!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.50,0:01:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Akko!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.58,0:01:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're totally different things.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.21,0:01:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly, they are entirely separate.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.52,0:01:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,These children stole a tart, not a pie!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.52,0:01:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tarts are three times as expensive as pies!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.18,0:01:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Badcock, there's no need\Nto bring up the price with the students...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.06,0:01:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep your mouth shut, Professor Ursula. {must resist calling it a piehole}{## u dun good}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.85,0:01:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In the first place, you eat far too much already!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.07,0:01:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna Nova has enough financial issues as it is, yet you eat through the food budget like fools!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.23,0:01:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're only hungry because you're so stingy with the budget!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.06,0:01:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's menu was potato salad, mashed potatoes,\Nand French fries—three kinds of potato dishes!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.76,0:01:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you not be satiated after eating so many potatoes?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.45,0:01:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Potatoes get digested too quickly!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.92,0:01:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That is quite enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.42,0:01:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only did you steal a pie, but you back-talked a teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.21,0:01:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, then! We just so happen to be receiving a food shipment tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.63,0:01:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You are to unload the trucks.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.74,0:01:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You are also to take remedial lessons\Nwith Professor Ursula in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.80,0:01:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I understood, Professor Ursula?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.64,0:01:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.51,0:01:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait! I can't do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.88,0:02:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make our punishment something else!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go to the city tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.60,0:02:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.24,0:02:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything else you want!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.42,0:02:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll clean the goblins' ears or wash the troll baths—anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.52,0:02:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, even Akko is repenting!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.69,0:02:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at her!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.79,0:02:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise to be good! \NI'll even massage your shoulders!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.07,0:02:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you, Lotte?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.15,0:02:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you, let me to go the city tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.92,0:02:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.16,0:02:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not! You are categorically\Nforbidden to leave tomorrow!{## TLC "you three"?}{given context it doesn't matter}
