Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.06,0:03:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Lotte?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.78,0:04:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.98,0:04:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No good, her eyes are all clouded over.
