Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.82,0:04:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, what's so special about tomorrow?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.01,0:04:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a release event for the new {\i1}night fall{\i0} volume in the city tomorrow! {phew, it says it in the flyer}{## gotta say i hate the all-lowercase name}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.81,0:04:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.63,0:04:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too close.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.77,0:04:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}night fall{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.28,0:04:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, {\i1}night fall{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.81,0:04:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Heard of it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The title, at least.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.89,0:04:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}night fall{\i0} is a series of novels that have been a huge hit all around the world!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.55,0:04:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Belle, a high school science teacher who got cold feet\Njust before her wedding, visits a manor house {I suppose Belle is correct, I'm used to Bell because of pretty rhythm}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.94,0:04:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and falls though a mysterious portal to the past, where she meets a handsome man named Edgar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But then she finds out Edgar is a vampire!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.29,0:04:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Belle is thrust into a tempest that shakes the very foundations of history!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.26,0:04:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story of love,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.84,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,adventure,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.76,0:04:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,thrills,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.89,0:04:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,conspiracy,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.97,0:04:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,friendship,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.97,0:04:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and youth!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.41,0:04:51.97,Default,,10,10,0,,{\an8}It's a literary epic encompassing every genre imaginable\Nand presented as a historic fiction novel for girls!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.97,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until now, there have been 364 volumes.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.44,0:05:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And tomorrow, the memorable 365th novel is finally being released!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.15,0:05:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, my favorite character is Edgar's rival, the werewolf Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is more troubled and charming than him!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.03,0:05:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.70,0:05:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.41,0:05:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't {\i1}night fall{\i0}'s author constantly\Ngetting trolled on the internet? {literally "flamed" in the net sense, but nobody uses that word correctly anymore}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.67,0:05:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! The author, Annabel Crème, is a witch who's been writing the series for 120 years.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.47,0:05:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's never shown her face in public before,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.38,0:05:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but she'll finally reveal herself at tomorrow's event!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.39,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, sounds cool.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.64,0:05:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be selling original goods at the event, and all the fans are going to dress up in costume! {the word cosplay comes later}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.78,0:05:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't go...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.36,0:05:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's all over. All of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.10,0:05:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... over...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.02,0:05:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she's lost it. {I'm serious}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.66,0:05:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She isn't taking this well.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.42,0:05:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel horrible for Lotte.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.01,0:05:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're the one to blame.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's my fault?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.91,0:05:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't stolen that tart,\NLotte would've been able to go to the city.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.36,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I won't be able to make it. {from the message}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.98,0:06:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll check out Annabel's MyStage. Maybe she's posted something about tomorrow. {myspace/facebook probably}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.50,0:06:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There they go again.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.23,0:06:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw man, I wish I could go see Annabel\Nin person, even if only for a second.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.65,0:06:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I just came up with the best plan ever!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.70,0:06:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all potatoes again...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.57,0:06:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the last of them.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.01,0:06:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're finished.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.71,0:06:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do this.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.18,0:06:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.72,0:06:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your help.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, and goodbye!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.01,0:06:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.52,0:06:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hannah and Barbara, yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.15,0:06:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to be back by six.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.18,0:07:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitching a ride will get us right to the city. {there's an underlying feeling in this line of 'sensei can say what she wants about us not going, because this will take us there anyway'}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.81,0:07:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a genius!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.49,0:07:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.43,0:07:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot about Professor Ursula's lesson!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.87,0:07:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko, you can't make an omelette\Nwithout breaking a few eggs.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrifices are a necessary evil.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.69,0:07:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard her.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.83,0:07:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it'll work out somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.59,0:07:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay girls, we'll be spending some time together for a fun lesson today.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.82,0:07:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko! Akko!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost past the city.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.34,0:07:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! Oh, Lotte, you're in cosplay!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.67,0:07:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.67,0:07:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks great!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.99,0:07:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.44,0:07:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the city!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.33,0:08:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we're back on foot.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.88,0:08:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The magic dies off quickly once we leave school grounds.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.46,0:08:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.73,0:08:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All the city streets are filled with {\i1}night fall{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a dream!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.82,0:08:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.60,0:08:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there! It's the pirate waiter from volume 158! {lit 'waiter on the pirate ship', but he's clearly a pirate}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.58,0:08:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And over {\i1}there{\i0} is the bagpiper who dies in battle in volume 220!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.65,0:08:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the old loan shark who only shows up for one line in volume 37!{'one moment'}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.44,0:08:37.10,Default,,10,10,0,,Isn't that one of the 20 existing toothbrushes that came bundled with the magazine version as a bonus 100 years ago?{just way too wide}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.10,0:08:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy it for any amount you wish! \NGo on, name your price!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.62,0:08:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.69,0:08:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, excuse me!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.85,0:08:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.86,0:08:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.74,0:08:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you Great Ben, the clock tower\NBelle lived in at the very beginning of her journey?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.57,0:08:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can trust anyone with a costume like yours with my life!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.57,0:08:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the first person to recognize me. {this is seriously like a real anime con, I'm feeling it}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.19,0:08:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I would, it's common knowledge!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.25,0:09:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly girl, we're already friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.28,0:09:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.96,0:09:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on around here? {the normalfag shows up}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.84,0:09:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is an event for {\i1}night fall{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That worthless drivel?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.14,0:09:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How stupid must you be to dress up like that as an adult?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.94,0:09:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we stick around just to see\Nhow stupid they are for ourselves?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.71,0:09:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.70,0:09:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that it?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, it's over there!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.23,0:09:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.19,0:09:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, girls!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.57,0:09:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is packed!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.03,0:09:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The crowd's bigger than I expected.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.89,0:09:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What made you become a fan of {\i1}night fall{\i0}, Lotte?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.07,0:09:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened back when I was a child.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.70,0:09:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My family ran a small magic item shop.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.85,0:09:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, some of the local kids started teasing me because I was a witch.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.32,0:09:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when I first encountered\N{\i1}night fall{\i0} at the library.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.24,0:10:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a reflection of myself in the vampire clan \Nthat was despised by humans and got hooked.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.44,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I realized eventually that the werewolf Arthur was only making passes at Belle to get Edgar's attention.{## uh oh...}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.42,0:10:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't get that out of my mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.29,0:10:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I realized it, my own worries\Nseemed trivial in comparison.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.30,0:10:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there must be many more people like me\Nwho felt like they were saved after reading this.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.19,0:10:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, couldn't really catch that! Say it again?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.24,0:10:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to {\i1}night fall{\i0}'s special event!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.12,0:10:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,To commemorate the release of {\i1}night fall{\i0}'s 365th volume,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.59,0:10:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the author Annabel will make her first-ever public appearance!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.07,0:10:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give it up for Annabel Crème!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! {\i1}She's{\i0} the writer?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.50,0:10:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she too young, even for a witch?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.61,0:10:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not just young, she's a kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.10,0:10:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she using magic to look like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.01,0:10:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.60,0:11:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Annabel! Can we have a word from you\Nfor your fans who have gathered here today?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.09,0:11:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.91,0:11:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A word for your fans!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.06,0:11:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.63,0:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who asked for a word.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.81,0:11:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So cold...{## meh}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cheeky brat.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.77,0:11:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.77,0:11:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, let's move on to our next segment.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.50,0:11:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}night fall{\i0} quiz show!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.80,0:11:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Every question was personally made by Annabel to test your limits!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.32,0:11:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever manages to take first place will be awarded a fabulous prize from Annabel herself!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Question one!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.68,0:11:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's a softball.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.46,0:11:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the new address of the company that made the gloves given to Belle by Grandma Hii?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.75,0:11:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You know this, Barbara?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no! I was just stretching my arm...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The fastest person was that red-hooded young lady!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.82,0:11:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,North Grampianshire, 43-5 White Street!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.26,0:11:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.33,0:11:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.19,0:11:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep on going!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Edward M. Winter!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.27,0:11:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,23678.9965!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.99,0:11:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Area code!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.90,0:12:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hexamine, potassium nitrate, and aqueous hydrogen peroxide. {literally homemade explosive}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,79 years and 2 months old.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.86,0:12:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finally down to our last two contestants.\NWhich of them will claim victory?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.87,0:12:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you happen to be GreatBen810?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.33,0:12:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she made it to the end.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.54,0:12:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, you can do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.75,0:12:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.79,0:12:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's Lotte!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko and Sucy are here too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.13,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,Lotte! Do your best!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, time for our final question.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.34,0:12:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Annabel Crème's mother learned piano\Nfrom a certain teacher as a child.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.92,0:12:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Her husband's father's favorite bakery is named...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.74,0:12:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Somerset Bakery!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.71,0:12:41.11,Default,,10,10,0,,...and in that town there is a botanical garden. \NWhat is the name of the third flower in the planted area?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.98,0:12:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was that really in there?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.11,0:12:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What volume was it written in?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.66,0:12:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.53,0:12:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like even Lotte's stumped by this one.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think it's a rose...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.50,0:12:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not a narcissus either...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.97,0:13:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hydrangea...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.43,0:13:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hydrangea!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.30,0:13:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.70,0:13:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.14,0:13:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We have our lucky winner!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please step forward.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's all tensed up.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.24,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she'd be! I mean, she's right in front of her idol.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.85,0:13:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Annabel's present is her favorite fountain pen!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You must really love {\i1}night fall{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.59,0:13:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.90,0:13:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll gladly accept this.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.97,0:13:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the next Annabel.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.85,0:13:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.63,0:13:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}night fall{\i0} wasn't written by just one single author. I'm the twelfth Annabel.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.17,0:13:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've accepted it, you're the thirteenth.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.07,0:13:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't write, then your beloved {\i1}night fall{\i0} ends today.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.35,0:13:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like she's disappeared. What a staple of Annabel Crème.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.14,0:13:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's these unpredictable twists that make {\i1}night fall{\i0} so irresistible!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.98,0:13:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A round of applause!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.10,0:14:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's all the time we have!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.98,0:14:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Didn't that seem kinda sudden?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.80,0:14:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty unnatural.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.90,0:14:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, she really got me there.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A magic item for teleportation...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea what to do after she vanished.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.74,0:14:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.38,0:14:27.17,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(605,605)\fnGriffin\c&H1A1A23&\3c&H000000&\fs60\blur0.5\pos(1012,69)}Little Witch Academia
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:27.17,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(605,605)\fnGriffin\bord3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs60\blur0.5\pos(1012,69)\1a&HFF&\t(0,605,\1a&H00&)\t(4525,5130,\1a&HFF&)}Little Witch Academia
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.44,0:14:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find her anywhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.74,0:14:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Think she's outside?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.81,0:14:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.76,0:14:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.72,0:14:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Annabel disappearing wasn't part of the show. It looks like she used this.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.97,0:14:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.74,0:14:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A magic item.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.77,0:14:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it's more like a toy anyone could use.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Annabel isn't a witch!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.94,0:14:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.98,0:14:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely have to find her!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.63,0:14:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me look!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.29,0:14:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.90,0:14:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Annabel? Annabel!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Annabel?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.16,0:14:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Annabel!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.60,0:14:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find Annabel!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.34,0:14:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mushroom. {fuckin laughed my ass off at this}{## i snickered loudly}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Annabel!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Annabel, where are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.46,0:15:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mushroom.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.06,0:15:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Find her?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she wasn't anywhere I looked. What now?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.85,0:15:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you need to find her so bad?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.51,0:15:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, {\i1}night fall{\i0} wasn't written by a single author.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.33,0:15:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was written by generations of people\Nwho inherited this fountain pen.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.47,0:15:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the fountain pen Annabel just gave to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.37,0:15:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.09,0:15:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that means you're gonna be\Nthe next writer of {\i1}night fall{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.98,0:15:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't return it, then yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.59,0:15:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great, Lotte!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.31,0:15:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.76,0:15:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It means Annabel passed the torch to you! {lit. told you to write the continuation}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.39,0:15:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.70,0:15:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get to write your favorite story yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.17,0:15:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dream is about to come true!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.52,0:15:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never asked for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.00,0:15:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that. You love {\i1}night fall{\i0} so much!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that's not it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.72,0:15:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.00,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand why you want to be like Chariot, {lit. 'be Chariot', not 'be like'}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.72,0:15:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've never wanted to be like Annabel.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.63,0:15:59.73,Default,,10,10,0,,I don't want to do the same thing the person I look up to does.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She can do things that I can't.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.49,0:16:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I just enjoy cheering on people like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.86,0:16:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I need to find Annabel as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.77,0:16:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is that fountain pen really old?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.41,0:16:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard that it's been used to write ever since the first chapter.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.07,0:16:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's that old, don't you think it should have a faerie?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.98,0:16:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.13,0:16:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte can talk to the faeries of old items.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.22,0:16:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.27,0:16:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too surprised.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Faeries dwell within old things.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.88,0:16:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned how to do it as a kid from my witch grandma.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.76,0:16:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not sure if it's possible here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.91,0:16:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere else.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.75,0:17:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you. My name is Lotte Jansson.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.48,0:17:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know where Annabel is.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.93,0:17:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.92,0:17:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd it say?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.39,0:17:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it doesn't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.79,0:17:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.76,0:17:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But listen, it said that this fountain pen chooses each successive writer of {\i1}night fall{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.25,0:17:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The current Annabel was chosen by this pen too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.29,0:17:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems that she isn't confident in her own abilities.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.26,0:17:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She only held today's event to look for a successor herself.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.99,0:17:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And she ended up choosing you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.15,0:17:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't accept that! {\i1}night fall{\i0}'s only been\Ngetting more interesting by the volume!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.33,0:17:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That means that the current Annabel's stories are amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.31,0:17:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never accept a {\i1}night fall{\i0} written by anyone except her!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.07,0:17:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, let's go tell her that!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.88,0:17:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.42,0:17:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way Annabel could quit writing\Nafter hearing that from you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.80,0:17:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.99,0:17:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering how much you love Annabel, you should be able to figure out where she'd go.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where Annabel would go?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.08,0:18:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah! Places she likes!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.70,0:18:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well, things she likes...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.11,0:18:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hydrangeas?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.66,0:18:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a bunch blooming over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.02,0:18:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's close!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.78,0:18:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the same.{## tattun is savage af}{i no rite}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.49,0:18:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I should head home now...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.17,0:18:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Even if you beg, I won't take it back!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.93,0:18:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That fountain pen belongs to you now!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.67,0:18:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you should be the one to have it.\NIt chose you for your talent.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not talented at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.69,0:18:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's been saying that the latest\N{\i1}night fall{\i0} books have been a train wreck.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.15,0:18:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I never expected Arthur to go to space...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.61,0:18:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,See?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.33,0:18:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised, but he's been unconsciously wanting to go to space for the longest time.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.18,0:18:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like when his Oedipus complex\Nwas revealed in the past.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.66,0:18:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Experts have been predicting this for ages!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something every fan knows!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.83,0:19:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We've always been waiting for this development!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.25,0:19:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just what a small part of the fanbase thinks.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.72,0:19:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I started writing,\NI've been flamed like crazy.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.97,0:19:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now {\i1}that's{\i0} only a small part of the fanbase.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.69,0:19:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The prison arc, the chapter when Belle caught a nuke with her bare hands,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.73,0:19:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and the saga of them aiming for the a capella world championship were all really interesting!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.65,0:19:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like, how could you possibly not enjoy all that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.82,0:19:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I wrote those because\NI thought they were interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.65,0:19:30.38,Default,,10,10,0,,But how am I supposed to stand back up when they say "stop writing" and "this sucks" and call each new volume worthless?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.38,0:19:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.55,0:19:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your favorite book?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.77,0:19:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Which book do you like the most?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.59,0:19:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Volume 363 when—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.12,0:19:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The one where Edgar lends Arthur his shoehorn?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.16,0:19:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I knew I wanted to write that one since I started!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.25,0:19:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Edgar hands over the shoehorn\Nwith his left hand, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.23,0:19:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,His clan believes that the left hand is a symbol of life.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.89,0:19:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And he handed him the shoehorn he received from his father with his left hand! That means—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.91,0:19:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.67,0:19:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I never realized!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.29,0:19:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.36,0:19:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.53,0:20:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a prodigy if you can\Nwrite that subconsciously.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.89,0:20:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew up reading {\i1}night fall{\i0}, so I really love it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.18,0:20:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the same for me. I think there are kids like that all over the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.69,0:20:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're the only one who loves it more than anyone and also has the ability to add to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.78,0:20:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stopped writing, then the real\N{\i1}night fall{\i0} would be gone forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.99,0:20:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you can write the {\i1}night fall{\i0} of our time.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.05,0:20:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you can be Annabel.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.33,0:20:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I really do want to write!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.71,0:20:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}night fall{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I saw her!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.95,0:21:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're crazy.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.26,0:21:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious! The cosplayer Lotte was talking to entered the leyline ahead of us!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be a Luna Nova student!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.13,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I presume you're prepared.{## little snitch academia}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.27,0:21:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.84,0:21:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a handshake from Annabel, but now\NI'm getting all covered in troll grime.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.43,0:21:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you were even her fan before.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.57,0:21:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares if I'm a secondary? {'niwaka' was thrown around a lot for kyoani fans a few years back}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.89,0:21:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, you can find all sorts of people in this world.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.19,0:21:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned a lot today.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.01,0:21:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking about Annabel? Didn't I tell you she was amazing?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.13,0:21:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean you! You don't want to be like the person you admire, you want to support them.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.29,0:21:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never considered that before.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.50,0:21:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I still think you missed a big opportunity.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.12,0:21:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still saying that?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.33,0:21:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I'm glad it ended well, Lotte.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.29,0:21:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm really glad.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.64,0:22:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be spoiled on the story if I wrote it myself,\Nso there'd be nothing to look forward to.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.57,0:22:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Was that your actual reason?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.16,0:22:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how it goes. Let's hurry up\Nand finish cleaning already.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.39,0:22:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,GreatBen810, aren't you excited for the next release?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.57,0:22:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I start reading?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.78,0:22:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.33,0:22:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save it until later.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.35,0:22:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
